This technical specification builds upon the default Next.js file structure and focuses specifically on the Ikig-AI Landing Page. By detailing the individual components, functions, and variables, it provides a clear and comprehensive guide for developing the landing page according to best practices. By following this structure, developers can create a responsive and visually appealing landing page that effectively showcases the Ikig-AI app.
